{
  "title": "Beat Bank",
  "children": [
    {
      "title": "Overview",
      "lines": [
        "~100 fixed drum",
        "patterns across many",
        "genres. No randomness.",
        "",
        "Pick a pattern and it",
        "prints one bar into",
        "Move's step sequencer.",
        "That's it."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "How to use",
      "lines": [
        "The menu has just:",
        " - Pattern",
        " - Swap Module / None",
        "",
        "Open Pattern -> a list.",
        "Scroll to a pattern and",
        "land on it: it splats",
        "one bar into Move (name",
        "+ genre shown).",
        "",
        "Scroll to another to",
        "print a different one."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Setup for printing",
      "lines": [
        "1 Slot MIDI FX mode ->",
        "  Schw+Move; Receive",
        "  Ch = the drum track.",
        "  Mute the slot.",
        "2 On Move: arm Record",
        "  + start playing.",
        "3 Pick a pattern -> it",
        "  records into the",
        "  current Move clip.",
        "",
        "Move must be playing +",
        "recording to capture."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Add Your Own",
      "lines": [
        "Patterns are plain",
        ".beat text files. Drop",
        "your own in:",
        " UserData/schwung/",
        "  beatbank/patterns/",
        "",
        "See _HOWTO.txt there",
        "for the format."
      ]
    }
  ]
}
